Package lolwut

The package involving the mechanics behind the game of Lolwut.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
Enemy The abstract class that represents a Lolwut enemy.
FlyingEnemy A class that represents an Enemy that flies through space.
Item A class that represents an item that the Penguin can pickup.
LevelMaker A class that creates the Platforms for Lolwut.
LolwutBrain  
Penguin The class that represents the player.
PhysicalObject An abstract class that represents all physical objects that can be displayed in Lolwut.
Platform A class that represents platforms that can be stood on by the player and by enemies and items
PointItem A class that represents items to get the player points.
Portal A class that represent the portals used to end the game and the fake portals to distract the player.
PowerUpItem An item that powers up the Penguin.
ScoreIOManager The class for reading and writing high scores to files.
WalkingEnemy A class that represents enemies that walk on platforms.
